ur using mark price divergence from spot indices. The shared order book architecture means funding rates apply uniformly across all frontend DEX partners accessing Orderly's liquidity. Settlement occurs automatically in USDT with positions marked-to-market against the aggregated order book. Cross-chain nature allows arbitrageurs to compare funding rates against NEAR and Ethereum-based exchanges simultaneously."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
